<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Aug1917"><font color="red">8 August 1917</font>, <cite>Letters II</cite> (JJ to Grant Richards):  &hellip; oblige me by wiring &hellip; whether you agree to 15 November as date of publication of <cite>Exiles</cite> &hellip; it will allow me to get on more quickly with my novel <cite>Ulysses</cite> which, if all goes well, I hope to have ready for publication next year.</div>
